  "2404800": {
    "name": "Idle Medieval Tavern",
    "steam_appid": 2404800,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/efcb77e247a13b706b232a82d3e75b05.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/efcb77e247a13b706b232a82d3e75b05.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/efcb77e247a13b706b232a82d3e75b05.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为旅馆老板，你的旅程从组建和训练一支英雄团队开始。你深入大陆，寻找勇猛的战士，难以捉摸的破坏者和独具慧眼的游侠。在你的指导下，这些技能高超的人们成为一支强大的团队。他们依靠专业技能和精心挑选的装备，踏上了寻求名利，保护无辜和消灭邪恶的危险旅程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/bbba82fd02fbe9256a45ecf8a7d835f0.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/bbba82fd02fbe9256a45ecf8a7d835f0.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/bbba82fd02fbe9256a45ecf8a7d835f0.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在你的引导下，这些技能娴熟的人形成了一支强大的团队。他们依靠专门的技能和精选的装备，踏上了追求名誉和财富的艰险之旅，他们在路上保护无辜，消除邪恶。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/65a025888750f100a5331109397e99d9.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/65a025888750f100a5331109397e99d9.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/65a025888750f100a5331109397e99d9.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着你的英雄声名远播，你的酒馆也会随之壮大。解锁新的房间和设施，将那个朴素的酒馆转变成一个充满活力的活动中心。美食的香气弥漫在空气中，顾客们聚集在餐厅，而娱乐室里则是扔刀比赛的刺激与兴奋。你的旅馆演变成一个华丽的避难所，豪华的卧室装饰着精美的艺术品和狩猎奖杯，欢迎疲惫的旅行者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/d4c7ca0a1f16e258faa8ec5a81c56e66.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/d4c7ca0a1f16e258faa8ec5a81c56e66.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/d4c7ca0a1f16e258faa8ec5a81c56e66.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>美食的香气弥漫在空气中，顾客们聚集在餐厅，而娱乐室里则是扔刀比赛的刺激与兴奋。你的旅馆演变成一个华丽的避难所，豪华的卧室装饰着精美的艺术品和狩猎奖杯，欢迎疲惫的旅行者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/2a7efb217310c9109ecef1b777ab6218.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/2a7efb217310c9109ecef1b777ab6218.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/2a7efb217310c9109ecef1b777ab6218.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>但这只是你旅程的开始。每一次的成功都会激励你建立传奇的旅馆帝国，每一家都比上一家更加繁华。从繁华的市场小镇到王国的偏远角落，你的酒馆拥有独特的氛围、娱乐和美食，吸引着来自四面八方的旅行者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/af007f3dc07cd6b17ddc86595bb197b2.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/af007f3dc07cd6b17ddc86595bb197b2.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/af007f3dc07cd6b17ddc86595bb197b2.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>随着你卓越的酒馆名声传播，来自遥远的土地的商队纷纷抵达，渴望进行贸易并补充他们的供应。你敏锐的谈判技巧为你的旅馆带来丰厚的利润，确保其持续的发展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/a8756c8946be2620aa25a60a38d7f762.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/a8756c8946be2620aa25a60a38d7f762.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/a8756c8946be2620aa25a60a38d7f762.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这兴旺的生意中，你的酒馆成为了雇佣兵的灯塔，他们被友情和机遇的承诺所吸引。每个新的盟友都会使你的公会的声望上升，有更多的英雄响应号召，踏上即使是最危险的任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/31551573134dbe13594309dd3e683d6b.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/31551573134dbe13594309dd3e683d6b.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/31551573134dbe13594309dd3e683d6b.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这款迷人的闲置游戏中，你所做的每个决定都会产生深远的影响，因为你正在努力建立最强大的旅馆帝国。你是否能挑战成功，成为传奇的旅馆老板，将自己的名字刻入历史？你的传奇旅程的故事等待着你……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/ee76f3ade6687d0114ef26f498ea3ace.poster.avif?t=1699451915\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/ee76f3ade6687d0114ef26f498ea3ace.webm?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404800/extras/ee76f3ade6687d0114ef26f498ea3ace.mp4?t=1699451915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
